            <div id="solutions-menu" class="mega-menu" data-mega-menu hidden>
              <div class="mega-menu-inner">
                <section class="featured-column">
                  <p class="menu-label">Advisory playbooks</p>
                  <h2>Targeted engagements</h2>

                  <p>
                    Diagnose the operational causes of adoption failure before
                    adding more technology, automation, or process overhead.
